<author>hạny̱ ạlḥnạwy̱, rwmạny rzq</author>
<title>ậdy ḥyạtnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (ylạ yạ ṣḥby ylạ yạ ạ̉ṣḥạby nḥḍr mʿ bʿḍ ạlqdạs
 ḥlw yswʿy ḥlwh knysty ḥlwh ṣlạtnạ wyạ ạlnạs)2
 1-(mạ ạ̹ḥnạ ạ̹mbạrḥ rwḥnạ lạ̉bwnạ wạ̉bwnạ ạ̉kẖd ạ̹ʿtrạfạtnạ
 wạ̹dạnạ ḥl ʿsẖạn ntnạwl wnslm lfạdynạ ḥyạtnạ)2
 2- (wạ̉ḥnạ kmạn fy ạlbyt hnṣly wnrnm ạ̉ḥly̱ ạltrạnym
 whạ nqrạ̉ fy ạ̹njylnạ tmly ʿhd jdyd ạ̉w ʿhd qdym)2
 3-(ậdy ḥyạtnạ wyạ yswʿnạ byh ntʿlm ḥbh bḥbh
 ạ̹zạy qlb yswʿ bysạʿd lmạ tkwn fy bynạ mḥbh)2</lyrics>
</song>